    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## PB - Cron Callbacks & Reminders\n\n**Runs every 15 minutes**\n\n### 3 parallel tracks:\n\n**Track 1 - Callbacks (top row):**\n- Fetch records where callback_datetime is within next 15 min\n- Trigger VAPI outbound call for each\n- Mark callback_ejecutado=true\n\n**Track 2 - 24h Reminders (middle row):**\n- Fetch citas happening tomorrow\n- Send SMS reminder\n- Mark recordatorio_24h=true\n\n**Track 3 - 1h Reminders (bottom row):**\n- Fetch citas happening in 60-75 minutes\n- Send SMS reminder\n- Mark recordatorio_1h=true\n\n### No Wait nodes used - cron handles timing\n### All SMS via Telnyx (Psycoboost sender)"
      },
